(2) 

Definition of a dependent of a NATO-1, 2, 3, 4, 5, or 6.

 For purposes of employment in the United States, the term 

dependent

 of a NATO-1, 2, 3, 4, 5, or 6 principal alien, as used in this paragraph, means any of the following immediate members
